  "title": "Securing Gen AI Apps with Entra 3/4",
  "contentHtml": "In this episode Michael and Gladys talk with guest Sharon Chahal&nbsp;\n                  (\n                     <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/sksandhu'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>\n                  ) \n                  about monitoring and auditing when building GenAI applications. We also cover other related topics.\n                  <br>\n                  We also discuss Azure Security news about API Security Posture Management, Azure Key Vault in China, Azure Data Studio retirement, new least privilege permissions in Graph and more.\n\n                  <br><br>\n\n                  <!-- Insert episode info from rss.com into NNNNNN and TTTTTT which is the episode number and the title -->\n                  <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/1968211?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"The Azure Security Podcast\" frameborder=\"0\"><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/1968211/\">GenAI3</a></iframe>\n\n                  <!-- Links to transcription and news articles -->\n                  <h5>Links</h5> \n                  <ul>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/1968211/#transcript'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-book\"></i></a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/blog/microsoftdefendercloudblog/boost-security-with-api-security-posture-management/4372385\">Boost Security with API Security Posture Management</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates?id=472065\">Azure Key Vault Premium, featuring FIPS 140 Level 3 Hardware Security Modules (HSMs), is accessible in China. </a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://blog.fabric.microsoft.com/en-US/blog/service-principal-support-for-fabric-data-warehouse/\">Service principal support for Fabric Data Warehouse</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://devblogs.microsoft.com/azure-sql/azure-data-studio-retirement/?utm_source=dlvr.it&utm_medium=twitter\">Azure Data Studio Retirement</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/merill/status/1887089269325619394\">Avoid granting super privileges like Directory.ReadWrite.All and User.ReadWrite.All to apps</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/merill/status/1762671638099947824\">Block Device Code Flow in Microsoft Entra ID Conditional Access</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/?searchterms=tls\">Azure Updates for TLS</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/dns/dnssec\">DNSSEC overview</a></li>\n                     <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href=\"https://devblogs.microsoft.com/identity/eng-connect-feb-25/\">February 2025: A look at the latest Microsoft Entra key feature releases, announcements, and updates</a></li>\n                  </ul>"
